        {
            "type": "list",
            "content": {
                "list_type": "text_list",
                "list_items": [
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "1. 建立图像源，并为OCRMax工具提供您需要对其进行分类的字符的示例图像。"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "2. 在显示屏中选择Current.InputImage图像。"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "3. 选择感兴趣区域的图形并对其进行修改以使其紧紧围绕字符串，如下所示："
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                163,
                95,
                662,
                146
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/33a1ecefad319417ba47076c2c84204ce6f53b4e425830d614536c58ce8cfca8.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                189,
                155,
                678,
                344
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "4. 单击“提取行”以使该工具对字符串进行分段并尝试区分单个字符。在大多数情况下，该工具可以正确识别各个字符符号，如下所示："
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                161,
                355,
                611,
                391
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/12028e581fd8bc05e72a7266b9726984ba66e61d342e6b8df09f69702081eb58.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                189,
                401,
                670,
                521
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "在某些情况下，该工具将根本无法执行分割，或者无法正确地正确分割图像，如以下示例所示："
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                186,
                533,
                778,
                548
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/53668c92e4f82602975aeb3f3c0ddc27bffdcf1235347d6f19abc21ef94383ad.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                189,
                557,
                670,
                657
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "如果该工具没有显示任何分割结果，请尝试调整区域图形，并在字符串周围给它半个字符的宽度，然后再次单击“提取线”。在继续下一步之前，该工具应至少能够执行部分分割。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                186,
                668,
                840,
                696
            ]
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "5. 使用“期望的文本”字段输入区域图形中包含的字符，然后单击“自动分段”。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                164,
                93,
                774,
                111
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "“Tune”选项卡应显示分段的字符串，并在每个字符下方带有一个标签，如下所示："
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                196,
                120,
                805,
                136
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
